text_importexport_content: Lapha ungangenisa futhi uthumele amabhukumaka akho ngefomethi ye-Netscape.
text_help_content1: Amabhukhimakhi Umphathi uhlelo lokusebenza olusiza ukugcina nokuhlela amabhukumaka e-inthanethi.
text_help_content2: Ukwakha ibhukumaka elisha, noma ifolda entsha, cindezela uphawu "lokuhlanganisa": khetha phakathi kwebhukhimakhi nefolda, faka isihloko bese ekugcineni i-URL, bese ucindezela ukonga ukugcina izinguquko, noma ucindezele okuthi susa ukususa ibhukumaka, noma emuva ukweqa izinguquko kepha ugcine ibhukumaka.
text_help_content3: Cindezela inkinobho "vula" eduze kwebhukhimakhi ukuvula i-URL ehlobene.
text_help_content4: Cindezela inkinobho "engeza" ngaphakathi kwefolda ukwengeza into entsha kuyo.
text_help_content5: Kuwo womabili amabhukhimakhi namafolda, cindezela inkinobho "hlela" ukuwashintsha, cindezela inkinobho "hlela emuva" ukushintshanisa isikhundla nento yangaphambilini, cindezela inkinobho "qhubekela phambili" ukushintshanisa isikhundla nento elandelayo, cindezela "hambisa phezulu" inkinobho ukukhipha into kufolda lapho ikhona njengamanje, noma cindezela inkinobho "yehla uye phansi" ukuhambisa into ngaphakathi kwefolda engezansi elandelayo.
text_help_content6: Kumenyu yezilungiselelo, efinyeleleka ngemuva kokuchofoza kusithonjana se- "izilungiselelo", ungafihla noma ubonise izinkinobho zokuhlela, ukunyakaza nokwengeza. Kungenzeka futhi ukuthi ushintshe ulimi lwesixhumi esibonakalayo somsebenzisi.
text_help_content7: Ukungenisa noma ukuthekelisa amabhukumaka, cindezela isithonjana sokungenisa / sokuthekelisa. Ifomethi ye-HTML Netscape Bookmarks iyasekelwa, ngakho-ke kungenzeka ukungenisa amabhukumaka akhishwe yiziphequluli ezinkulu zewebhu. Lapho ungenisa amabhukhimakhi asuka kufayela, amabhukumaka wamanje azosuswa futhi abhalwe phansi.
text_help_content8: Umphathi wamabhukhimakhi yi-Progressive Web Application, okusho ukuthi isebenza ngaphakathi kwesiphequluli. Uma uyifaka, ngenkathi izingxenye zesiphequluli zingakhonjiswa, isebenza ngaphakathi kwesiphequluli. Amabhukhimakhi agcinwa endaweni yokugcina yesiphequluli sesizinda samabhukhimakhi.marcoparrone.com. i-localStorage isebenza kahle ngeziphequluli ze-Chrome, Edge neFirefox. Ezinye iziphequluli zingasusa isitoreji sendawo ngemuva kwesikhathi esithile. I-Android ngokuzenzakalela isebenzisa i-Chrome, iWindows ngokuzenzakalela isebenzisa i-Edge. Umphathi wamabhukhimakhi okwamanje awasekelwa kumikhiqizo ye-Apple. Ngenhloso yokusiza ukuvimbela ukulahleka kwamabhukhimakhi, kuphakanyiswa ukwenza ibhekhaphu usebenzisa ukusebenza "kokuthekelisa", njalo lapho wenza izinguquko ezithile ongafuni ukulahlekelwa zizo.
text_about_content3: I-SOFTWARE INIKEZELWA "NJENGOBA INJALO", NGAPHANDLE KWESIQINISEKISO SONKE UHLOBO, BONISA NOMA UFAKELWE, KUHLANGANISWA KODWA AKUNAMKHAWULO EZIQINISEKISWA KWEZOKUTHENGISANA, UKULUNGELELWA KWENHLOSO ETHILE KANYE NOKUNGABONI. text_about_content4: LENKONZO KUNGASE KUQUKETHWE UKUHUMUSHA OKUNIKEZELWE NGU-GOOGLE. I-GOOGLE IKHALA IZIMPAWU ZONKE EZIPHATHELENE NEZINULELO, UKUBEKA OKUQUKETHWE NOMA OKUFAKIWE, KUFAKA IZIMPAWU ZOKUQINISEKISA, UKUTHEMBEKA, NANOMA YILUPHI IZIQINISEKISO ZOKWENZA UMSEBENZI, UKULUNGELELWA KWENJONGO ETHILE NOKUNGABONI.
text_about_content5: Lolu hlelo lokusebenza lwewebhu luhunyushelwe ukuzilungiselela usebenzisa isoftware yokuhumusha enikwa amandla yi-Google Translate. Kwenziwe imizamo enengqondo yokunikeza ukuhumusha okunembile, noma kunjalo, akukho ukuhumusha okuzenzakalelayo okungaphelele futhi akuhloselwe ukufaka esikhundleni sabahumushi abangabantu. Ukuhumusha kunikezwa njengesevisi kubasebenzisi bewebhusayithi ye-marcoparrone.com, futhi kunikezwa "njengoba kunjalo." Ayikho iwaranti yanoma iluphi uhlobo, noma eveziwe noma esetshenzisiwe, enziwa ngokunemba, ukwethembeka, noma ukunemba kwanoma yiziphi izinguqulo ezenziwe ngesiNgisi ziye kolunye ulimi. Okunye okuqukethwe (njengezithombe, amavidiyo, i-Flash, njll.) Kungahle kungahunyushelwa ngokunembile ngenxa yemikhawulo yesoftware yokuhumusha.
text_about_content6: Umbhalo osemthethweni yinguqulo yesiNgisi yewebhusayithi. Noma ikuphi ukungafani noma umehluko owenziwe ekuhumusheni akubophi futhi akunamphumela osemthethweni wokuhambisana noma wokusebenzisa ngenhloso. Uma kuba khona imibuzo ehlobene nokunemba kolwazi oluqukethwe kuwebhusayithi ehunyushiwe, bheka inguqulo yesiNgisi yewebhusayithi okuyiyona nguqulo esemthethweni.
